what is the meaning of life

The meaning of life is a complex and philosophical question that has been debated by humans for centuries. Different cultures, religions, and individuals may have varying perspectives on this question. Some believe that the meaning of life is to seek happiness and fulfillment, while others think it involves spiritual or religious purposes. Ultimately, the meaning of life can be subjective and may vary from person to person.
